The Comprehensive Guide to Inform 6 Programming
===============================================

This guide aims to be the definitive resource for learning and 
mastering the Inform 6 programming language, guiding readers from 
basic concepts to advanced techniques for crafting interactive fiction 
(IF) games. It is intended to replace the Inform Designer's Manual.

